dct_title_s: Waterford Township, New Jersey Feasibility Plan
dct_description_sm: Aerial photographic map labeled Exhibit C of the Waterford Township Feasibility Plan. In addition to street names, the map is labeled with locations of a pumping station, a Green Acres Project and a proposed waste water treatment center.
